How-To-Repeat: Run usleep() in a tight loop on a system, it will eventually hang.  I found that if I disconnect and replug in a FC port to cause LDT callout cycle, the box would hang pretty quickly (just got to get my sleep program on the same bucket as isp_ldt()).
